headline: Epilepsy Foundation of America Welcomes Accomplished Communications Executive to National Board of Directors
summary: BOWIE, Md., July 10, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The Epilepsy Foundation of America (EFA) is proud to announce the appointment of Daryl Drabinsky, distinguished communications and corporate affairs executive, to its National Board of Directors. Drabinsky brings extensive leadership experience in digital innovation, reputation management, and brand transformation across healthcare, technology, and global business sectors to the Foundation.
